  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495700/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764929468\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495700/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764929468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2495700/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764929468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>FLOWFALL is a challenging depth perception-based arcade game where you must fit the correct shapes into the correct gates as you fall. On a whim you can swap between 4 different shapes that each have a specific gate. Touch anything and the game is over, how long can you last? Set a high score using the in game timer!<br><br>Experience an amazing 15 song synthwave soundtrack! <br><br>A unique concept for the puzzle arcade genre,  fall through 8 different stages and prove you can FLOW!",
  "about_the_game": "FLOWFALL is a challenging depth perception-based arcade game where you must fit the correct shapes into the correct gates as you fall. On a whim you can swap between 4 different shapes that each have a specific gate. Touch anything and the game is over, how long can you last? Set a high score using the in game timer!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExperience an amazing 15 song synthwave soundtrack! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nA unique concept for the puzzle arcade genre,  fall through 8 different stages and prove you can FLOW!",
